Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:51.40,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}You were right here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.40,0:20:52.44,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}你曾在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:52.44,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}You were right here
