Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.90,0:21:02.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}是啊 从心脏到指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:02.78,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}そう、心臓から指先まで
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.78,0:21:06.66,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}都渴望和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:06.66,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}あなたに触れたい
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.66,0:21:10.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}想要守护你 想要在你身旁不离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:10.33,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}守りたい 隣にいたい
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.33,0:21:14.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}「直到重逢那日」
