Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.38,0:21:16.55,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}漫无目的的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:16.55,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}行く宛もないけど
