Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.38,0:21:18.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}{\an7}{\c&000000\3c&ffffff\4c&ffffff\blur4\bord5}却再次 沿着你的足迹寻觅
